#: ../../source/joint.rst:2
msgid "Joint"
msgstr "关节"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:11
msgid "Component of Joint"
msgstr "关节的组成部分"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:12
msgid ""
"Within rigid Body modification interface, press \"C\", a rigid body will "
"be created at position of the bone. If the bone has a parent, a joint "
"will be created at the head of the bone to connect the parent bone, the "
"child bone can rotate and move around the joints. The axis in the joint "
"settings means the local axis of the bone (The local axis of the bone "
"can be set to display in the armature properties armature->Data-"
">Viewport Display->Axes). The center of mass of the rigidbody will be "
"fixed at the tail of the bone, so the behavior of collision as a single "
"rigidbody will be a bit strange without a parent bone."
msgstr ""
"在刚体修改模式中，按“C”，将在骨骼位置创建刚体。 如果骨骼有父骨骼，则会在"
"骨骼的头部创建一个关节来连接父骨骼，子骨骼可以围绕关节旋转和移动。 关节设"
"置中的轴指的是骨骼的局部轴（骨骼的局部轴可以在骨架属性armature->Data-"
">Viewport Display->Axes中设置显示）。 刚体的质心将固定在骨骼的尾部，因此"
"如果没有父骨骼，作为单个刚体的碰撞行为会有点奇怪。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:14
msgid ""
"Joint between two rigidbody can be seen as a spring, two rigidbody is "
"connected by spring force."
msgstr "两个刚体之间的连接可以看作是一个弹簧，两个刚体通过弹簧力连接。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:17
msgid "Joint Properties"
msgstr "关节属性"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:19
msgid "**Stiffness**: determine the stiffness of the spring."
msgstr "**刚度**：定义弹簧的刚度。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:21
msgid "**Damping**: determine the damping of the spring."
msgstr "**阻尼**：定义弹簧的阻尼。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:31
msgid ""
"**Angle Limit**: hard constraint, which limits the rigidbody relative "
"rotation. Due to the limitations of PhysX, only symmetrical angle "
"constraints can be set. If you want to constrain only one side, you can "
"add a kinematic rigid body to the parent bone and place it on the side "
"you want to constrain to constrain the movement of the dynamic rigid "
"body."
msgstr ""
"**角度约束**：硬约束，限制刚体相对旋转。 由于PhysX的限制，只能设置对称角"
"度约束。 如果只想约束一侧，可以在父骨骼上添加kinematic刚体，并将其放置在"
"要约束的一侧，以约束动态刚体的运动。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:33
msgid ""
"**Distance Limit**: hard constraint, which limits the rigidbody relative "
"movement."
msgstr "**距离约束**：硬约束，限制刚体相对位移。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:35
msgid ""
"**Hard constraints**: the distance constraints and angle constraints set "
"in the panel. This is the constraint range you tell physx should not "
"exceed. If too much force pushes him away from the hard constraint "
"range, it will be subject to a large reaction force trying to return."
msgstr ""
"**硬约束**：面板中设置的距离约束和角度约束。 这是您告诉 physx 不应超过的"
"约束范围。 如果用力太大将他推离硬约束范围，就会受到很大的反作用力试图返"
"回。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:37
msgid ""
"**Soft constraints**: The springs connecting rigidbodies can be called "
"soft constraints, that is, the stiffness and damping in the panel. It "
"represents that the rigidbodies will be affected by the spring within "
"the range of hard constraints."
msgstr ""
"**软约束**：连接刚体的弹簧可以称为软约束，即面板中的刚度和阻尼。 它表示刚"
"体在硬约束范围内会受到弹簧的影响。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:39
msgid ""
"The rotation of the bones in edit mode is important for joint, keep "
"attention to it when you are creating armature."
msgstr "骨骼编辑模式下的的旋转对于关节很重要，在创建骨架时请注意这一点。"

#: ../../source/joint.rst:41
msgid ""
"The initial position of the joint constraint is based on the rest "
"position of the bones. You can reset bones to init position by pressing "
"Alt+R Alt+G Alt+S."
msgstr ""
"关节约束的初始位置基于骨骼的静止位置。 您可以通过按 Alt+R Alt+G Alt+S 将"
"骨骼重置到初始位置。"
